	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree with your comment.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>The problem in your argument, however, is that the ORG, all things being equal, will always be ahead of the DWF or the DE (or any other class for that matter) when it comes to melee stats (STA included).<br><br>For instance, you kept the ORG at his base STA, while the DWF needed to have some crusty to get his STA up to the ORG level.  Is that fair to the ORG?  Why doesnt he get the benefit of armor / stats?<br><br>Further, even if someone maxed out their STA with the ORG, so that the other races could catch up, then all the better.  With his high base STA, he doesn't need as much gear to bring it up as high, so he has freed up other slots to increase other stats.<br><br>I am generally fond of all races &amp; classes.  And I group with every class that I can regardless of race.  However, the numbers are what the numbers are &amp; the numbers clearly demonstrate that a ORG will, all things being equal, tank better than any other race.  Is it to a material degree?  Im not sure.  But it is better.<br><br>=)<br><br>Lunatic<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
