	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay, it maybe too early this morning to answer this, because Im not really sure what your asking.&nbsp;&nbsp;That's most likely my fault.  <br><br>First off, you do not have to be grouped with the person that you are trying to help find their corpse.  But in the event that you are already grouped with them and they die, to target them, what I do is click on the person, or click on their health bar.  Then since they are in your target box, when you cast Locate corpse the spell will search the zone for their corpse. <br><br>Hope that helps.  <br><br>Scyinide<br>Shadow Knight<br>of the 41st Season<br>Sins of the Serpent(Officer)<br>Tallon Zek<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
