	   <tr><td colspan=2>ok, so i feel ur pain, i have a lvl 42 sk (he is my main) so i have been in ur situation, lets talk about cash first. u have 500p, thats not to bad for ur lvl and this being ur first char. no w how can we raise this orer the next few lvls so u can get ur DF armor. I would suggest that u start hunting in WW OT, and FM on kunark, let me explain, u can hunt giants in WW at the fort for cash, they drop some coin up to a plat or 2, they also drop weapons and caps that can be sold to vendors for between 10p to 40p, giants also drop forest loops which sell to players for between 250p to 300p and u can always sell the loop to a vendor for at least 200p. next u can start hunting in OT (great exp here) sarnaks drop plat! chickens drop beaks that sell for at least 1p, a char. can make at least 20-30p in just a small amount of time in a group in the OT (and as i said, its also great exp). and then there is FM which is alot like WW, LOTS OF GIANTS. I also belive that weapons and forest loops drop more often in FM but reamber its a higher lvl zone than WW.<br><br>just my 2 cents<br>dregg lvl 42sk<br>grimm lvl 29 wiz<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
